        "title": "Ireland Defeat India by 1 Run in Second T20 International",
        "summary": "In Men&#8217;s Cricket, Ireland defeated India by 1 run in the second and final T20 International of the two-match series in Belfast last night. Hosts Ireland set a target of 155 runs for India. Put into bat, Ireland made 154 runs, losing eight wickets in the stipulated 20 overs. In reply, India could score only […]",
