        "title": "Canada Beat South Africa 1-0 in FIFA World Cup Knockout Stage",
        "summary": "In the knockout stage of the FIFA World Cup, Canada beat South Africa 1-0 for its first knockout match victory at Los Angeles in the United States. Stephen Eustáquio of Canada scored the goal in the second minute of second-half stoppage time. Co-host Canada hung on with strong defensive play in the final minutes […]",
